OL,3,CMother of son who was killed in the
OL,4,CNottingham attacks speaks of her grief
OL,6,FA mother whose son was killed during
OL,7,Fthe Nottingham attacks has spoken
OL,8,Fabout the heartache she still feels.
OL,10,F19-year-old Barnaby Webber, 19-year-
OL,11,Fold Grace O'Malley-Kumar and school
OL,12,Fcaretaker Ian Coates were killed in
OL,13,FJune 2023.
OL,15,FValdo Calocane, who had been diagnosed
OL,16,Fwith paranoid schizophrenia before the
OL,17,Fattacks, was sentenced to an
OL,18,Findefinite hospital order in January
OL,19,F2024, after admitting manslaughter by
OL,20,Fdiminished responsibility and
OL,21,Fattempted murder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
