OL,3,CMother of son who was killed in the
OL,4,CNottingham attacks speaks of her grief
OL,6,FFor the past two years, Barnaby's
OL,7,Fmother Emma says she has been on a
OL,8,Frollercoaster of emotions, from
OL,9,Fdespair to anger and mental exhaustion.
OL,11,FAhead of the 2nd anniversary of the
OL,12,Fattacks tomorrow (13th June), Emma has
OL,13,Fspoken of her grief and ongoing fight
OL,14,Ffor justice.
OL,16,FEmma said: "It's very difficult to see
OL,17,Fgroups of students, especially boys.
OL,18,FAnd ironically, sometimes from behind
OL,19,Fbecause you let yourself wish,
OL,20,Fpotentially, it might be him. Such is
OL,21,Fthe sadness and the power of that loss.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
