OL,3,CMother of son who was killed in the
OL,4,CNottingham attacks speaks of her grief
OL,6,FShe recalls the heartache of having to
OL,7,Fsay goodbye to her child just a month
OL,8,Fafter his death.
OL,10,FEmma added: "It's the wrong order of
OL,11,Fevents. And to have to even think
OL,12,Fabout planning your own child's send-
OL,13,Foff - we called Barney's funeral at
OL,14,Fthe time - is unfathomable."
OL,16,FTo help navigate her way through the
OL,17,Fgrief, Emma has weekly intense trauma
OL,18,Ftherapy sessions. She's also become a
OL,19,Fpatron of the new National Grief
OL,20,FAdvice Service based at Grantham in
OL,21,FLincolnshire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
