OL,3,CMother of son who was killed in the
OL,4,CNottingham attacks speaks of her grief
OL,6,FEarlier, Barnaby's father, David and
OL,7,Fbrother Charlie, and Grace O'Malley-
OL,8,FKumar's parents visited the spot where
OL,9,Fthey were killed to lay flowers.
OL,11,FIt was something Emma found too
OL,12,Fpainful to endure then. But something
OL,13,Fshe's determined to remedy tomorrow.
OL,15,FThe families of Barnaby Webber, Grace
OL,16,FO'Malley-Kumar and Ian Coates have
OL,17,Fbeen fighting for answers as to how
OL,18,FCalocane, who has paranoid
OL,19,Fschizophrenia, was free to kill.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
