OL,6,FEarlier this year, the Prime Minister
OL,7,Fannounced there would be a public
OL,8,Finquiry into the attacks.
OL,10,FThe families of the Nottingham attack
OL,11,Fvictims say they've told the Health
OL,12,FSecretary they want the names of staff
OL,13,Finvolved in treating killer Valdo
OL,14,FCalocane to be made public.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
