OL,3,CMother of son who was killed in the
OL,4,CNottingham attacks speaks of her grief
OL,6,FHe said: "I've seen too many examples
OL,7,Fof where people have put protecting
OL,8,Fthe reputation of the NHS or
OL,9,Findividual hospitals over protecting
OL,10,Fpatients and I'm calling time on that
OL,11,Fkind of culture.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
