OL,3,CMother of son who was killed in the
OL,4,CNottingham attacks speaks of her grief
OL,6,F"So, I am naturally in more favour of
OL,7,Ftransparency, what I've got to way up
OL,8,Fin this case is in terms of naming
OL,9,Findividual clinicians involved in the
OL,10,Fcare of Valdo Calocane, whether I'd
OL,11,Factually be creating a different sort
OL,12,Fof risk, which is a risk when
OL,13,Fclinicians make mistakes which they
OL,14,Fwill that they don't come forward or
OL,15,Fwhen people are worried when they
OL,16,Fdon't speak up.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
