OL,3,CMother of son who was killed in the
OL,4,CNottingham attacks speaks of her grief
OL,6,F"So, that's what I'm weighing up, it
OL,7,Fis not a straightforward decision, but
OL,8,FI've listened to the families this
OL,9,Fweek and I'm now going to consult with
OL,10,FNHS leaders and I will be reporting
OL,11,Fback on a decision in the coming
OL,12,Fweeks."
OL,14,FEmma said they get strength and solace
OL,15,Ffrom the care and compassion from the
OL,16,Fcommunity and others.
OL,18,FShe said they still get letters and
OL,19,Fmessages from people in and around
OL,20,FNottingham to let them know they are
OL,21,Fthinking of them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
