OL,6,FNext month, Barnaby and Grace would've
OL,7,Fgraduated from the University of
OL,8,FNottingham and an event will take
OL,9,Fplace to give them honorary degrees.
OL,10,FEmma said she may not attend as it
OL,11,Fwould be too painful.
OL,13,FThe victims' families are welcoming
OL,14,Fanyone who wants to join them on a
OL,15,Fmemorial walk tomorrow.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
