OL,6,FThey are being invited to consider
OL,7,Fwearing something green or gold, the
OL,8,Funiversity's sports colours, or red,
OL,9,Fthe shirt colour of Ian Coates'
OL,10,Fbeloved football team, Nottingham
OL,11,FForest.
OL,13,FThe theme is a day of quiet
OL,14,Freflection. A day to say to three
OL,15,Fpeople whose lives were brutally cut
OL,16,Fshort, you may be gone, but you'll
OL,17,Fnever be forgotten.
